et": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待男子顺路搭同事回家出车祸，法院判决赔偿同事家人 90 万？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，福建厦门。海沧区法院审理了一起纠纷案，男子戴某下班时顺路搭载同事王某回家，行驶至某路段时碰撞到路边墙体，造成同事王某当场死亡。交警认定：戴某负事故全部责任，王某不负事故责任。戴某与王某家人对此均无异议，王某家人要求戴某赔偿 130 万余元。 本案中，戴某与死者王某系同事关系，事故车辆系非营运机动车，戴某搭载王某并未向其收取费用，且事故认定书中并未发现戴某存在故意或明显重大过失的情形。法院酌定戴某承担 70% 的赔偿责任，判决戴某赔偿王某家人因本起交通事故造成的各项经济损失 90 万余元。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-59918310fa28b9abcc6aba083db29e58_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/511124171"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iud/Mv7WFvKlEEAMaCDc1ODY0NjUwIKXn+I4GMAI4MUAPcgk1MTExMjQxNzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1642043254.899843", "card_id": "Q_510945073", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些网文作者必备的数码产品？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c4f65b2956566e3823361b9af25d32fa_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/510945073"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iud/Mv7WFvKlEEAMaCDc1ODI0OTIxINey844GMAE4JEAQcgk1MTA5NDUwNzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1642043254.9002264", "card_id": "Q_510861997", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 130}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "能留下一句你喜欢的文案吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-b2544a6cb787d59ea303c942fd5d7a72_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/510861997"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iud/Mv7WFvKlEEAMaCDc1ODA2NTI3IM76744GMAA4yQFAEXIJNTEwODYxOTk3eACqAQliaWxs